        <section class="teacher-content">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-8 col-sm-12">
                        <h1>Meet your faculty at Saint Louis University</h1>
                        <p>Your faculty at Saint Louis University have a wealth of experience and come from diverse backgrounds; many have studied internationally themselves. They have a passion for teaching, encouraging students to think on a deeper level and going beyond academics to solve real-world problems. This is why they are the perfect mentors to help you work towards achieving your academic potential.</p>
<p>To make sure you are ready to graduate, your faculty will guide you to make the most of your higher education journey, ensuring that you feel supported along the way. This experience will include:</p>
<ul>
<li>access to a student center, career services and involvement in study groups</li>
<li>a holistic approach to teaching subjects</li>
<li>classes of no more than 30 students for English language teaching</li>
</ul>

                    </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12">
                            
